appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Thank you for downloading Ticketing Boxoffice mobile application, we are committed to delivering new features and keep on enhancing the application for better user experience.
In this version we have added new features in the event details to display more information about the event you are purchasing, example icons for 18+.and social distancing requirements.
Moreover we have activated the listing on Events groups to load in pages of 10 events.
